params._pancakeLocker: address of the pancake locker contract

params._baseAmount: amount of base tokens to be locked
params._baseToken: token received for sold launchpad token
params._saleAmount: amount of sale tokens to be locked
params._unlockDate: timestamp to unlock the locked lp token
params._withdrawer: address allowed to withdraw token after unlock date

params._token0: one address of the pancake pair base tokens
params._token1: the other address of the pancake pair base tokens

lockLiquidity(address,address,uint256,ui.notice: locks iquidity by creating a liquidity pair (LP) with base and sale token, sending liquidity amount of both tokens to the LP and locks the minted LP token with PancakeLocker contract.
